<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تَفْسِيرُ السُّورَة<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم , طه}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٩٥:</span> قَالَ عِكْرِمَةُ،<span class="c5"> وَالضَّحَّاكُ:</span> بِالنَّبَطِيَّةِ: <span class="c2">(أَيْ طَهْ)</span>: يَا رَجُلُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [طه: ١]</p> </div>